Package: corrdiscdist
Title: Inference and simulation on correlated discrete distributions
Version: 0.1.0-1
Date: 2026-03-31
Description: Implementation of simulation (wrapping around RcppDist) and inference (wrapping around mvtnorm) for selected correlated discrete distributions (negative binomial, binomial, ordinal multinomial). Provides interfaces for R, C++, JAGS and TMB (maybe).
